    "Clinical_Features": {
      "text": "Altered mental status\nAphasia\nAtaxia\nHemiparesis\nHemiplegia and\nvisual field disturbances\nSeizure\nCranial nerve palsies\n(rare)\nCervical spine involvement (rare)",
